  "body": "With a brand new fresh clone of commit `d7d790725ba2d70e8e5ce229feefb9d0af7065c7`, this curl command returns no data and 'method handler crashed.'\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\"params\":[\"0xc62d9410b73b18d767fe32df91e6336c5d563eceee49c55c56df65bfeb4b966d\"],\"id\":1,\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}' http://localhost:8545\r\n```\r\n\r\ncall stack\r\n\r\n```\r\nERROR[04-23|12:46:14.514] RPC method eth_getTransactionReceipt crashed: runtime error: invalid memory address or nil pointer dereference\r\ngoroutine 106 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*callback).call.func1(0xc000394980, 0x19, 0xc003303d50)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/service.go:200 +0xbd\r\npanic(0x10196c0, 0x1aa35f0)\r\n        runtime/panic.go:965 +0x1b9\r\ngithub.com/holiman/uint256.(*Int).ToBig(0x0, 0xc0000da000)\r\n        github.com/holiman/uint256@v1.1.1/conversion.go:32 +0x55\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands.marshalReceipt(0xc0032aa540, 0x12dbdf8, 0xc000238000, 0xc0003aaeb0)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands/eth_receipts.go:282 +0x87\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands.(*APIImpl).GetTransactionReceipt(0xc000142c80, 0x12cbe90, 0xc000143680, 0xd7183bb710942dc6, 0x6c33e691df32fe67, 0x5cc549eece3e565d, 0x6d964bebb\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands/eth_receipts.go:226 +0x37f\r\nreflect.Value.call(0xc00012d000, 0xc000388528, 0x13, 0x1161b28, 0x4, 0xc0003aad70, 0x3, 0x3, 0xc0003aada0, 0xc0003a93f8, ...)\r\n        reflect/value.go:476 +0x8e7\r\nreflect.Value.Call(0xc00012d000, 0xc000388528, 0x13, 0xc0003aad70, 0x3, 0x3, 0x0, 0x0, 0x10efda0)\r\n        reflect/value.go:337 +0xb9\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*callback).call(0xc0003878c0, 0x12cbe90, 0xc000143680, 0xc000394980, 0x19, 0xc0003a93f8, 0x1, 0x1, 0x0, 0x0, ...)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/service.go:206 +0x2c5\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*handler).runMethod(0xc0001b4d80, 0x12cbe90, 0xc000143680, 0xc00034d1f0, 0xc0003878c0, 0xc0003a93f8, 0x1, 0x1, 0x1)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/handler.go:399 +0x8a\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*handler).handleCall(0xc0001b4d80, 0xc000216f60, 0xc00034d1f0, 0xc0014056c0)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/handler.go:347 +0x252\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*handler).handleCallMsg(0xc0001b4d80, 0xc000216f60, 0xc00034d1f0, 0x12c0601)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/handler.go:301 +0x1be\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*handler).handleMsg.func1(0xc000216f60)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/handler.go:142 +0x46\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*handler).startCallProc.func1(0xc0001b4d80, 0xc0003a93e0)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/handler.go:229 +0xd2\r\ncreated by github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc.(*handler).startCallProc\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/rpc/handler.go:225 +0x66\r\n```\r\n\r\nI'm going to try to fix this, as I need it for my testing.",
